{UTF-8}
Stock Level = INTEG ( Adjustment Rate, 50 )
	~ Unit
	~ 一阶负反馈：库存向目标追赶。最基础的调节回路，恒温器/库存补货/目标追赶通用结构。
	|

Target Stock = 100
	~ Unit
	~ 目标值（可改为外生政策变量）
	|

Discrepancy = Target Stock - Stock Level
	~ Unit
	~ 目标与现状的差距
	|

Adjustment Time = 5
	~ Month
	~ 调整时间常数：越大响应越慢
	|

Adjustment Rate = Discrepancy / Adjustment Time
	~ Unit/Month
	~ 每期调整量，驱动库存趋近目标
	|

INITIAL TIME = 0
	~ Month
	~	|

FINAL TIME = 60
	~ Month
	~	|

TIME STEP = 0.25
	~ Month
	~	|

SAVEPER = TIME STEP
	~ Month
	~	|

